					<div class="tool-container">
					  <div class="tool-card">
						<div class="tool-content">
						  <h3 class="tool-title">New market target lists & deep research</h3>
						  <p class="tool-description">Identifying lists of companies to start targeting in your new market & doing deep research on them is a daunting task. That’s where Dream comes in. Our agents research information across the internet (from sources like LinkedIn, Google, Crunchbase & others) so you have all the information needed to prioritise your outreach. </p>
						</div>
						<div class="tool-content">
						  <h3 class="tool-title">Identify the right prospect & contact information</h3>
						  <p class="tool-description">Finding the right person to target in a new market is a complex task - they may have different titles or simply be in a different language. Dream can determine who the best stakeholders are at those companies for you to target. Dream pulls in their profiles, as well as their contact information, so you can start to run outreach directly to the key people at those companies. </p>
